{"tid":624670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《網球撚入》點解費達拿可以稱霸網球界咁多年？","createTime":"2018-04-11T00:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T17:53:39.000Z","uid":150109,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d47017660333157f7ed898a777f6b06a6e9f1b18","tid":624670,"uid":150109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:31:04.000Z","msg":"我呢排睇翻網球發現佢ranking仲係top 4<br />\n我小學開始睇網球，睇到而家大學佢仲贏緊glad slam <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我記得佢有一兩年好似因為背脊有傷患而跌哂watt，以為佢會收皮，點知又比佢反彈<br />\n<br />\n啲後浪nadal Murray Djokovic 都好似開始收收地皮皮 究竟點解佢可以keep住咁多年高水準表現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 之前幾睇好Djokovic，點解近年好似無乜聲氣？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 記憶仲停留喺 nadal fed Murray Djokovic 嗰時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無睇好耐"},{"pid":"c7149fa6386a0b1f986023b875651c756839f9ff","tid":624670,"uid":150109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"同埋點解佢掟拍都咁型？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gz19hsMxPkQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGz19hsMxPkQ&d=6xk%2F9XeIPJjZF1upQV6olQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=abfdccfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gz19hsMxPkQ</a>"},{"pid":"daecaf21ac5ccfc194e47c8f7615ea9e7bc2a8c6","tid":624670,"uid":124726,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"Federer冇稱霸好耐啦 佢係keep得好 <br />\n但對上一次年終第一已經係2009年<br />\n近十年基本上係3+1+1格局<br />\n最強勢係djokovic 4次年終第一 二百幾週世界第一 都係2011年開始<br />\n仲有5個年終冠軍 除左大滿貢數量<br />\ndjokovic 其他數據係好過nadal<br />\n<br />\n舊年djokovic, murray, wawrinka因傷收例<br />\n基本上到宜家都未好返晒"},{"pid":"6fcc8eb1ddd826809ca9903a38d52ab90e8123de","tid":624670,"uid":73641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daecaf21ac5ccfc194e47c8f7615ea9e7bc2a8c6","tid":624670,"uid":124726,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"Federer冇稱霸好耐啦 佢係keep得好 <br />\n但對上一次